d_image\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer\" rel=\"noreferrer\" src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/100/v2-2bf8d3ecd0d456df8e71b0a7a9dfe285_r.jpg\" title=\"产品对比 2\"/></p>\n", "last_modified": 1782435167, "replies": 77, "id": 1222950}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_large.png?m=1726310276", "name": "games", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_normal.png?m=1726310276", "title": "游戏", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/games", "topics": 3341, "footer": "", "header": "Life is short, have more fun.", "title_alternative": "Games", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/b53b/3a3d/55_mini.png?m=1726310276", "stars": 2603, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 55, "parent_node_name": "computer"}, "member": {"id": 247937, "username": "Number13", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Number13", "website": "", "twitter": "", "psn": "", "github": "", "btc": "", "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10db/e863/247937_mini.png?m=1502358599", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10db/e863/247937_normal.png?m=1502358599", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/10db/e863/247937_large.png?m=1502358599", "created": 1502358493, "last_modified": 1502358599, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "coderwink", "last_touched": 1782441025, "title": "来吧，推荐出让你心动的鼠标吧，都 2026 年 6 月了，是时候更新一波鼠标了", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1222740", "created": 1782359161, "deleted": 0, "content": "我本人用的是 罗技 502 有线版，但是这个鼠标现在感觉有点重了，尤其我还是一个主打 fps 类游戏的玩家，而且它鼠标敏感度虽说可调，但是无法调整的很舒适，只有固定的几个档位。\r\n\r\n所以求讨论、求推荐，现在市面上的鼠标哪个更适合 fps ？\r\n\r\n* 参数：\r\n * 手型：大手、右手\r\n * 重量：轻量化\r\n * 是否有线：要求无线\r\n * 价位：肯定是好用便宜是最优解，但如果很好用，稍微贵一点也无伤大雅", "content_rendered": "<p>我本人用的是 罗技 502 有线版，但是这个鼠标现在感觉有点重了，尤其我还是一个主打 fps 类游戏的玩家，而且它鼠标敏感度虽说可调，但是无法调整的很舒适，只有固定的几个档位。</p>\n<p>所以求讨论、求推荐，现在市面上的鼠标哪个更适合 fps ？</p>\n<ul>\n<li>参数：</li>\n<li>手型：大手、右手</li>\n<li>重量：轻量化</li>\n<li>是否有线：要求无线</li>\n<li>价位：肯定是好用便宜是最优解，但如果很好用，稍微贵一点也无伤大雅</li>\n</ul>\n", "last_modified": 1782359239, "replies": 74, "id": 1222740}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_large.png?m=1747623725", "name": "random", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_normal.png?m=1747623725", "title": "随想", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/random", "topics": 4331, "footer": "", "header": "有的时候，可以停下来找找灵感，然后再继续。", "title_alternative": "Random", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/093f/65e0/59_mini.png?m=1747623725", "stars": 1314, "founder_id": 0, "aliases": [], "root": false, "id": 59, "parent_node_name": "v2ex"}, "member": {"id": 390537, "username": "Henryable", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/u/Henryable", "website": "https://blog.riveer.dpdns.org/", "twitter": null, "psn": null, "github": null, "btc": null, "location": "", "tagline": "", "bio": "", "avatar_mini": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f893f63bba7803d3762ebed5ff773f84?s=24&d=retro", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f893f63bba7803d3762ebed5ff773f84?s=48&d=retro", "avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/f893f63bba7803d3762ebed5ff773f84?s=73&d=retro", "created": 1552028488, "last_modified": 1552028488, "pro": 0}, "last_reply_by": "Crazy9527", "last_touched": 1782441008, "title": "V 站越到后面，靠签到领取的铜币会越来越少，被迫发帖讨要铜币", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/t/1222945", "created": 1782433496, "deleted": 0, "content": "V 站的铜币规则很有意思，每次领取的数目是随机的但有规律的，一开始平均每次有 10 几枚，连续签到 40 天左右之后，每次只能领 2 枚左右，为了获取更多的铜币，只能积极发帖，这种设计挺好的。", "content_rendered": "<p>V 站的铜币规则很有意思，每次领取的数目是随机的但有规律的，一开始平均每次有 10 几枚，连续签到 40 天左右之后，每次只能领 2 枚左右，为了获取更多的铜币，只能积极发帖，这种设计挺好的。</p>\n", "last_modified": 1782433847, "replies": 60, "id": 1222945}, {"node": {"avatar_large": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_large.png?m=1630643991", "name": "iphone", "avatar_normal": "https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c9f0/f895/8_normal.png?m=1630643991", "title": "iPhone", "url": "https://www.v2ex.com/go/iphone", "topics": 13001, "footer": "这里绝不讨论如何获得 iPhone 盗版软件、iTunes 黑卡之类。", "hea